{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_05_02",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 2話 麻奈のこれまで",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日　東京のレッスンスタジオ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day‚ at a lesson studio in Tokyo",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.333333300001,
          "startTime": 5.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-01.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん、レッスン終わったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ lesson's over!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今日はどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How was it today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.80606184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-04.m4a",
      "text": "って、カメラ覗いてるけど、まさか……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ you're looking through the camera‚ don't tell me…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8666660308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ドキュメンタリー番組用に撮影中だ\nリアリティーのある映像がほしいみたいだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm filming for the documentary.\nThey want realistic footage‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9999981243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-07.m4a",
      "text": "だからって汗だくなところ撮らないでよ～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So don't film me while I'm all sweaty~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0666652042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-02.m4a",
      "text": "ばかばか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Silly‚ silly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8000013987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "わ、悪い悪い。レッスン中の麻奈はかっこいいからな\n撮っておかないともったいないと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry‚ sorry. You look cool when you're in lesson mode‚ Mana‚\nso I thought it'd be a waste not to film it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5666602131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えー？　そっか、それなら仕方ないかな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Oh‚ okay‚ I guess that's fine then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4666606263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-04.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンの動画は許してあげる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll let you film the lesson!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5085089493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（ちょろい……）\n（実は撮られるの、まんざらでもないんじゃないか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's easy…）\n（I wonder if she actually doesn't mind being filmed?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4999935464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "といっても、使われるかは制作会社さん次第だけどな\nレッスンが終わったらインタビュー、いいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's up to the production company whether they actually use it.\nCan we do an interview after the lesson?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1333268798,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7700.0028928999955,
          "startTime": 55.8333297727
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-10.m4a",
      "text": "うん、でもちょっとだけ待って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ but give me a minute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.333327293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "水分補給してくる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to rehydrate…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.749086494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "慌てなくて大丈夫。今日は時間に余裕があるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't rush. We have plenty of time today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3999954855,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5766.666890899998,
          "startTime": 63.1666623764
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お待たせ！　いつでもいいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm back! Anytime's good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7666621521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_start-05.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、なんでも聞いちゃって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ ask me anything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1321566683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "よし、じゃあ始めるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ let's get started.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7333356853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんは、歌だけでなくダンスのレベルも\n高いですが、何かコツはあるんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-san‚ your dancing is just as good\nAs your singing‚ but is there some kind of trick to it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4000019387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "コツ……うーん、なんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A trick… Hmm‚ what could it be?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8666690186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_think-05.m4a",
      "text": "昔から体を動かすのは好きでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always liked moving my body ever since I was little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9742421464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "目を離したらすぐどっか行っちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My parents used to say I'd disappear if they took their eyes off me for a second.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8333311077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "元気過ぎて困ったって両親が言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I even got into trouble for being too lively.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.3417901194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "妹をいじめてる男の子をやっつけた時も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like that time I beat up a boy who was bullying my little sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4999977744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "最初は褒められたけど、その後すっごく怒られちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got praised at first‚ but then I got scolded like crazy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0782227106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも、妹のことをいじめるんだからしょうがないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But he was bullying my sister‚ so it couldn't be helped!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7666705445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-14.m4a",
      "text": "私の大事な妹に何するんだー！　って感じ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like‚ \"How dare you do that to my precious little sister!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9333236692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ、妹はね、赤ちゃんの頃から私の手を握ってくれたり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ and my sister‚ she'd hold my hand ever since she was a baby‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4333372112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-10.m4a",
      "text": "ちょこちょこ後ろをついてきたりして。もう可愛いの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And she'd always follow me around. She's so cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9424002507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "おいおい、いつの間にか\n妹さんのことばっかり語ってるぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ hold on‚ you're\nOnly talking about your sister now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9666716572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-05.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、ごめんごめん、ダンスの話だったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ sorry‚ sorry. We were talking about dancing‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.7333387371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "コツは、諦めないこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The trick is‚ never giving up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.172297705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_start-04.m4a",
      "text": "出来なかったことが出来るようになると",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I learn to do something I couldn't before‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4333382285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "凄く自信がつくの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get really confident.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1973332524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
